data.description: What a deal!! Beautiful ranch style home located in the highly desirable Antelope Ridge subdivision! One level living with 3 spacious bedrooms and an oversized 2 Car Attached Garage. Large primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom. Spacious eat-in kitchen with an abundance of natural light! Walk out onto your deck in the backyard and have a cup of coffee overlooking your beautifully landscaped yard. The amenities include a clubhouse with gym, pool, conference rooms, picnic areas, playground and tons of trails. Conveniently located near Marksheffel Rd and Powers Blvd. Property is on a land lease and included in the HOA already. This is truly a fantastic value and a rare find in today's market!! Don't miss this opportunity!
